title: The Cowboys Are The Browns
itunes:title: The Cowboys Are The Browns
description:
Colin explains why the Cowboys are a lot like the Browns, why he’s ok with the new college football rankings, where he thinks Ron Rivera might coach next, and the main problem facing Tom Brady right now. Guests include Albert Breer, Will Blackmon, Peter Schrager, and Marcellus Wiley.
